data.description: Charming 4 bed, 3 bath home in East Germantown, with modern updates. Enter into the main living area featuring hardwood flooring and an eye-catching decorative fireplace. Continue through the dining area, offering ample space for entertaining. The chef's kitchen is adorned with granite counters and island, along with stainless steel appliances. The kitchen also offers access to the rear staircase, laundry room, and convenient full bath with stall shower. The spacious rear yard is the perfect place for a summer BBQ. Downstairs, the finished basement offers an island with sink and bar stool seating. The basement is also accessible through a separate front entrance. Upstairs, the second floor features 3 bright & airy bedrooms and a full 3 piece hall bath. The third floor hosts the master suite, complete with 3-piece bathroom, including a jacuzzi tub. Located. Financing details, This property is eligible for the chip program, see attached flyer for details, no income limit, no PMI., no down payment, income waived. reach out for details. this property also qualifies for the  HomeReady Grant.
